<h3>Trip Details</h3>
<p>The trip started on <%= @trip.start_date %> and ended on <%= @trip.end_date %></p>
<p>The trip started at <%= @trip.start_station_name %>, and ended at <%= @trip.end_station_name %></p>
<p>The trip lasted <%= @trip.duration %> minutes</p>
<p>The trip was on bike# <%= @trip.bike_id %></p>
<p>The person taking the trip was a <%= @trip.subscription_type %></p>
<p>The trip zip code was <%= @trip.zip_code %></p><br><br>
<td>
  <form action="/trips/<%= @trip.id %>/edit" method="get">
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning btn active btn-sm" role="button" aria-pressed="true" value="edit">Edit</button>
  </form>
</td>

<td>
  <form action="/trips/<%= @trip.id %>" method="POST">
    <input type="hidden" name="_method" value="DELETE">
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger btn active btn-sm" role="button" aria-pressed="true" value="delete">Delete</button>
  </form>
</td>
<p><a href='/trips'>Back to the trip index</a></p>
